content: Hello,I am the founder of Stithulf. I have been working on the project "StithulfERC (SULFERC)" for a while.Project Description: Due to various factors such as COVID-19, Economic Policies, and Geopolitics, The current economic situation for everyday people is more unstable than ever before. Due to high inflation risks, Many central banks have risen their rates which is causing more pain for many normal people. We aim to ease up this economic pain by providing very low-interest loan services for individuals as well as institutions.The technical details regarding the project will be posted here soon.Token Tracker: https://etherscan.io/token/0x2277964ce25D22f9F12E1497181575d77037C0B3Official Website: https://stithulf.com/The Token is launching soon (Between 24th Feb to March Starting) and, The project will be launched by March Ending.
